  <acronym>CARCIK</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 1-2a Trial to Determine the Feasibility and Safety of a Single Dose of Transposon-manipulated Allogeneic CARCIK-CD19 Cells in Adult and Pediatric Patients With Relapsed or Refractory B-cell Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia, After Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
