  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children (1-17) and adults (18-75 years old);

          -  Relapsed or refractory adult and pediatric B-cell precursor ALL after HSCT;

          -  Evidence of CD19 tumor expression in bone marrow and/or peripheral blood by flow
             cytometry;

          -  Bone marrow with â‰¥ 5% lymphoblasts by morphologic assessment at screening;

          -  No evidence of overall aGVHD &gt; Grade I or chronic GVHD (cGVHD) greater than mild at
             time of enrollment and in the previous 30 days;

          -  No longer taking immunosuppressive agents for at least 30 days prior to enrollment;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with GVHD Grades II-IV;

          -  Any cell therapy in the last 30 days;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
